import numpy as np
import csv
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import matplotlib
for num in range(1, 9):# 运用for循环读取八个班的文件
    filename = "计190" + str(num) + ".csv"#创建以各班级为csv的文件名
    with open(filename,"r") as f:
        data = np.loadtxt(f,str,delimiter = ',')
    color = ['b','g','r']#用于折线的三种颜色
    class_name = "计190" + str(num)
    for i in range(3):#循环画出三种图
        plt.plot(data[1:,i+3], color = color[i])
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    plt.ylabel('成绩',fontproperties = 'SimHei')
    plt.title(class_name,fontproperties = 'FangSong',fontsize = 20)
    plt.show()

for a in range(3):#循环三列成绩
    scorelist_name = "scorelist" + str(a)
    scorelist_name = []
    for num in range(1, 9):
        for i in data[1:]:
            scorelist_name.append(int(i[3+a]))#追加每一个班的成绩到列表里
#     print(scorelist_name)
    Fail = 0
    D = 0
    C = 0
    B = 0
    A = 0
    for i in scorelist_name:
        if i < 60:
            Fail += 1
        elif i>= 60 and i < 70:
            D += 1
        elif i>= 70 and i < 80:
            C += 1
        elif i>= 80 and i < 90:
            B += 1
        elif i>= 90 and i <= 100:
            A += 1
    x = ["0-59", "60-69", "70-79", "80-89", "90-100"]
    y = [Fail,D,C,B,A]
    plt.bar(x, y, alpha=0.5, color = color[a], edgecolor='k')
matplotlib.rcParams['font.sans-serif']=['SimHei']
plt.title("学生成绩分布直方图")
plt.ylabel("频数")
plt.xlabel("区间")
plt.show()
